README

function.blockquote.php

toArray() converts a string into a multidimensional array. Every occurance of > at the beginning of a line will deepen its leven in the return array.
toQuote() converts the produced multidimensional array into a string, where each level will be surrounded by <blockquote> html elements.

Example input:

Hello.

> I am a quote
>> I am a nested Quote
> I'm back on level 1

Best regards

-----------------------------------------

Output:

<blockquote>
Hello.
<blockquote>
  I am a quote
  <blockquote>
    I am a nested Quote
  </blockquote>
  I'm back on level 1
</blockquote>
Best regards
</blockquote>